  "title": "Interior Sales Designer (Consult | Project Management)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Basic up to $2500 - $3500 + Commission + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Kallang</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working days: Monday to Friday</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 9.00am - 6.00pm</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Meet with clients to understand their design preferences, requirements, and project goals.</li>\n  <li>Designing &amp; Planning Floorplan Layouts</li>\n  <li>Consulting Clients with Material &amp; Colour Selection</li>\n  <li><strong>Managing the entire project from Start to Finish</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Client Management</strong></li>\n  <li>Coordinating with multiple sub-contractors while liaising and updating clients</li>\n  <li>Ensuring a smooth delivery of the project and meeting appropriate timelines</li>\n  <li>Other ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Design (Interior/Spatial) or equivalent.</li>\n  <li><strong>At least 1 year experience in Interior Design Sales.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG JYA YEE (R23119014)<br>\nEA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br>\nEA License No: 21C0492</p>",
